MyBroadband has partnered with Afristay to offer you a great prize: A 2-night stay for 2 people at an establishment of your choice. We will also throw in R1,000 spending money. Afristay has properties across South Africa and is known for its excellent service and no guest booking fees. Its accommodation portal also makes it very easy to organise your stay, from planning where you want to spend the night, to booking, arrival, and departure. To enter the giveaway, you must: The winner’s accommodation will be paid for in full, and they will also receive R1,000 spending money for the weekend. The competition will run until 26 May, and the winner will be announced on 27 May.